{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.EffectForwarder.restoreCont\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">EffectForwarder</span>.<span class=\"name\">restoreCont</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.EffectForwarder\">EffectForwarder</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Build a `DoElemCont` that unpacks the lifted body's result and resumes `origCont.k`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.EffectForwarder.restoreCont","kind":"def","line":275,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.EffectForwarder.restoreCont","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Control.lean#L275-L277"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.EffectForwarder.lift\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">EffectForwarder</span>.<span class=\"name\">lift</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.EffectForwarder\">EffectForwarder</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">elabElem</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a> → <span class